      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require extensive mechanical and cosmetic work to be roadworthy again. The engine has significant performance issues, and the transmission is failing, causing severe shifting delays. Additionally, the body shows heavy wear, including noticeable rust and multiple dents, while the interior requires a complete overhaul. This is strictly a project car or a candidate for parts.",
